Biographical Sketch of the Bell Family and Reminiscences.

John Bell, Sr., was born in 1750 in Halifax
county, North Carolina. He was a son of William
Bell, a thrifty farmer and prominent citizen.
John was given a good country school education,
and was brought upon the farm, where he acquired
industrious and steady habits in youth,
and grew to manhood noted for his indomitable
-----File: 040.png---------------------------------------------------------
